<bibRefCitation author="Kolesnichenko, K. A. &amp; Yakovlev, R. V." box="[445,830,1878,1904]" pageId="8" pageNumber="33" pagination="101 - 109" refId="ref9553" refString="Kolesnichenko, K. A. &amp; Yakovlev, R. V. (2004) Taxonomic notes on Melitaea phoebe ([Denis &amp; Schiffermuller], 1775) (Lepidoptera, Nymphalidae) from the south-western Mongolia with a description of a new subspecies. Helios, 5, 101 - 109, plates V - VI." type="journal article" year="2004">Kolesnichenko &amp; Yakovlev, 2004</bibRefCitation>
